'The shooting happened outside by her vehicle, right outside the back door and that's where Michael was shot,' Zanic told WTAJ.

'Words can't describe the scene ... heartbreaking,' he said.

Baree resident Olivia Ellenberger told the TV station she saw Mr Ayers fleeing the scene.

'This is the first time anything like this has happened since I lived here. It's different,' Ellenberger said.

